The player MUST use the arrow keys to control the car.
The car MUST have an acceleration comparable to a real vehicle. 
The player MUST NOT crash the car more than 3 times in a single race.
The player MUST go through every checkpoint before finishing the race.
The player SHOULD go through the checkpoints in order.
There MUST be at least 10 obstacles per race.
There SHOULD be around 15 obstacles per race.
There SHOULD NOT be more than 20 obstacles per race.
The player SHOULD stay on the track.
